data.description: PRICE REDUCED 5K!! Turn-key Ready! This Gorgeous 2 Bedroom home will dazzle and check all of the right boxes! A comfortable and well-appointed Living Room welcomes all upon entry. Plenty of seating is available for entertaining or daily comfort. Attractive easy-care tile flooring had been installed throughout. The Kitchen offers distinctive Granite Countertops to enhance lovely, crisp white cabinetry along with a beautiful Stainless Steel Refrigerator with peek-view door!! A bonus pantry is perfect for extra storage! Sliding glass door opens onto the back yard. The Livingroom offers more storage with a handy closet. A spacious Linen Cabinet can be found in the Hallway between rooms. Bathroom was tastefully remodeled with handsome sink base, granite countertops and complimentary bathroom fixtures. One of the Bedrooms offers its own private door to bathroom access. Lot is very large, Just installed a newly wood fencing around the property for more privacy. This fabulous home is conveniently located near area restaurants and is only 1.4 miles to the Oasis Visitor Center of the Joshua Tree National Park, and is located just 4.8 miles to the front gate entrance. This one is a no-brainer! GREAT FOR FIRST-TIME HOME BUYERS OR INVESTOR! DON’T MISS OUT! SUPER LOW TAXES! ABSOLUTELY NO HOA! MOVE IN READY AND IS A MUST SEE!!
